Comment: 0,0:01:29.98,0:01:29.98,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:32.57,0:01:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"No, you idiot. Military {\i1}drills{\i0}!"
Dialogue: 10,0:01:36.95,0:01:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your continued appreciation!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:49.33,0:01:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Um—
Dialogue: 10,0:01:50.04,0:01:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ask such dull questions!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:53.76,0:01:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, nobody asked anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:57.63,0:01:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My bad.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:59.68,0:02:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what were you saying?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.05,0:02:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you buy if you won the lottery?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.31,0:02:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,See, I knew it'd be something dull!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:07.89,0:02:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please. That's an easy one.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.48,0:02:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd save it a—
Dialogue: 10,0:02:11.06,0:02:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Anything to avoid being the kind of person \Nwho'd put all the money into savings.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.57,0:02:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, yeah. It's like, c'mon, dream big!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.53,0:02:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't think of anything worse.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.37,0:02:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}The kind of person who, if you ask them \Nwhat animal they'd want to come back as,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.83,0:02:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,would always say "human".
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.83,0:02:26.37,Alt,,0,0,0,,Hum—
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.87,0:02:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm, what's up, Marii?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:30.63,0:02:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, n-nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.79,0:02:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So what would you buy, then?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.13,0:02:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? I guess...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.96,0:02:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd pay off my debts.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.30,0:02:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Your dreams are awfully small \Nfor someone that spouted all that!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.97,0:02:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Paying it back is no different to saving it up!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.22,0:02:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a lot more urgent...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.72,0:02:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, spare me the sob story!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.39,0:02:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Three hundred million yen?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.77,0:02:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had three hundred million yen, I'd...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.11,0:02:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I would track down my missing mother.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.49,0:03:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, really...?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.28,0:03:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}If I won the lottery, I'd use the money \Nto hunt down the true culprit.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.33,0:03:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.08,0:03:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be great if you could catch them.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.67,0:03:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.67,0:03:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.34,0:03:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with the private conversation, guys?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.80,0:03:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Debt? Lost moms? True culprits?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.76,0:03:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all you can come up with?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.18,0:03:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The lottery lets you buy whatever your heart desires!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.55,0:03:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}One ticket costs three hundred yen. \NThat's crazy money!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.27,0:03:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}You can't fork out crazy money if your plan is \Nto spend your winnings on boring crap!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.44,0:03:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Kigu! What would you buy if you won?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.32,0:03:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna know!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.98,0:03:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell us!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.57,0:03:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you do?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.19,0:03:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Th-This is a lot of pressure...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.32,0:03:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd build a house out of my favourite candy!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.70,0:03:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so you!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.70,0:03:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You cutie.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.12,0:03:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As if.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.88,0:03:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\q2}I'm getting sick of playing into \Neveryone's expectations of me.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.38,0:04:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,One thing is for sure, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.22,0:04:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If I won the lottery, I wouldn't tell anyone about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.43,0:04:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, me neither.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.39,0:04:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Definitely not.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.43,0:04:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could it be?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.73,0:04:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Has one of us...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.65,0:04:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Already...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.27,0:04:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Won?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.94,0:04:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.74,0:04:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.45,0:04:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.49,0:04:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}did{\i0} get a new kimono recently!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.24,0:04:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Come into a little money, did we?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.33,0:04:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What're you getting at?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.50,0:04:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit the nail on the head, I'd say.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.42,0:04:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you? Didn't you arrive in a taxi today?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.38,0:04:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A taxi?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.30,0:04:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Highly suspicious.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.26,0:04:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It only cost the base fare!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.51,0:04:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I-If we're pointing fingers, I saw you, y'know!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.01,0:04:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You bought McD's without using a coupon!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.22,0:04:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,McD...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.31,0:04:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Without using a coupon...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.10,0:04:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}There's no way you'd do something so \Nextravagant if you hadn't won the lottery!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.69,0:04:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What about her?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.19,0:05:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She's got a holiday brochure in her purse!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.49,0:05:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for my grandma!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.36,0:05:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mess about with other people's purses!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.53,0:05:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see what everyone's got in theirs, shall we?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.24,0:05:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.66,0:05:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! She's been seeing films without using the Ladies' Day discount!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.66,0:05:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And she went to see [DDY] KimiKoe!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.63,0:05:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}There's no explanation for \Nthis kind of reckless spending!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.04,0:05:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh! Stop it!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.59,0:05:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop all this senseless fighting!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.17,0:05:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}You know what they say, \Nthere's no money in squabbling!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.84,0:05:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.72,0:05:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Rich people don't bother themselves with \Nthe petty concerns of regular people.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.39,0:05:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They're above that.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.47,0:05:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}In other words, that means that \Neveryone here must be totally broke.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.10,0:05:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But they also say "as stingy as a millionaire".
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.15,0:05:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you looking at me?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.40,0:05:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Fat cat!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.40,0:05:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Cut it out! Stop looking at me!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.78,0:05:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I just like snacking!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.41,0:05:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Wouldn't you expect a rich person to have \Nmore self-control and a really good body?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.00,0:05:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I ain't talking about you, big-heads!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.25,0:05:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If rich people don't squabble,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.54,0:06:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,what do they do when they have a disagreement?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.79,0:06:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They do argue, just in a more refined way.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.84,0:06:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}I simply do not understand these \Neconomically impaired people.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.47,0:06:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How very sophisticated of you.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.80,0:06:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}I say, good madam, perchance wherefore \Nwhat are you enspeakenestening about?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.77,0:06:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}I think you should perhaps mollify \Nyour obstrepepeperous tendencies.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.19,0:06:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Please ingest a portion of defecation.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.77,0:06:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.90,0:06:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,"Eat shit"?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.99,0:06:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}I reckon that when someone's wealthy, \Nit shows in intangible ways.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.45,0:06:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.99,0:06:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}For instance, after someone won the lottery, \NI'd expect them to change as a person.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.87,0:06:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting with the things they say.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.42,0:06:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You! Do you remember what you said the other day?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.79,0:06:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I—
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.55,0:06:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I respect my parents more than anyone!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.38,0:06:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Nobody says that kind of stuff \Nunless they're completely carefree!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.26,0:06:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Could it be that you're carefree \Nto the tune of three hundred million yen?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.10,0:06:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure what you—
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.47,0:07:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}It's elementary, my dear Marii. \NI've deduced the solution to this mystery.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.27,0:07:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're{\i0} the culprit!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.10,0:07:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.11,0:07:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Culprit? I think she means "winner".
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.27,0:07:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?! Just step forward already!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.07,0:07:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.11,0:07:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard something once.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.61,0:07:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}They say that even if lottery winners \Nkeep a low profile,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.62,0:07:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}pros will be able to smell \Nthe scent of money on them.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.54,0:07:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Pros?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.66,0:07:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Relatives you've never met before. \NSchoolmates from different classes.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.92,0:07:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are just parasites!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.59,0:07:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.97,0:07:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you got a moment to talk about the Lord?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.89,0:07:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's a pro, right on schedule.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.89,0:07:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She's sure to know which one of us is the rich one.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.85,0:07:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one of us do you want to convert the most?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.11,0:07:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is the lottery winner?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.73,0:07:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do I want to convert the most?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.24,0:07:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}The young lady most at risk \Nof falling into Satan's clutches is...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.24,0:07:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Her!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.54,0:08:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It ain't me!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.04,0:08:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\blur1.73}It ain't me!
Dialogue: 11,0:08:00.04,0:08:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\4a&HFF&\blur1.73}It ain't me!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.12,0:08:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It ain't me!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.20,0:08:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\blur1.73}It ain't me!
Dialogue: 11,0:08:00.20,0:08:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\4a&HFF&\blur1.73}It ain't me!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.29,0:08:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}It ain't me!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.71,0:08:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut your damn mouth!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.87,0:08:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need for violence!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.00,0:08:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The power was cut?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.79,0:08:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}You'd think a millionaire would \Nbe able to pay our bills on time.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.51,0:08:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's back on.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.22,0:08:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Retaliation?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.81,0:08:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One of us is a convert...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.56,0:08:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.94,0:08:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Attacked...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.36,0:08:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Marii?
Comment: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:34.95,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.91,0:08:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Talk about a panoramic view!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.74,0:08:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We're lucky it's so clear.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.16,0:08:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see for miles!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.33,0:08:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad we came.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.00,0:08:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.83,0:08:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we doing here?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.04,0:08:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, what are we doing here?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.13,0:08:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are we at Tokyo Tower?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.01,0:08:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't everyone go to Skytree these days?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.14,0:09:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Skytree isn't a tower, yeah? It's a tree.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.64,0:09:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.43,0:09:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokyo Tower all the way.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.52,0:09:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Its fan-like design is very auspicious.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.06,0:09:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Skytree is too skinny.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.61,0:09:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokyo Tower is 333 metres tall.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.03,0:09:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that a beautiful number?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.24,0:09:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,By comparison, Tokyo Skytree is 634 metres.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.57,0:09:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Are they trying to make it sound like "Musashi"? \NWhere's Kojirou's tower then?
Dialogue: 9,0:09:18.57,0:09:24.12,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs32\shad0\pos(33.333,18.667)}Note:
Dialogue: 9,0:09:18.57,0:09:24.12,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs29.333\bord2.667\shad0\pos(33.333,52)}The Japanese numbers 634 can be pronounced \Nlike the name of the famous swordsman "Musashi". \NKojirou is another swordsman who was famously \Ndefeated by Musashi.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.79,0:09:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They should have just gone for 666.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.12,0:09:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the mark of the devil!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.33,0:09:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Tokyo Tower's major shareholders are \Nthe Toei film company and Mother Farm.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.25,0:09:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I prefer Toei because of the film connection.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.09,0:09:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why Mother Farm? Sheep can't climb towers.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.01,0:09:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.72,0:09:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}When they're lost on the farm, \Nthey can use the tower to guide them home!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.68,0:09:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Uh, no. Mother Farm's in Chiba. \NYou can't see it from there.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.60,0:09:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}The tower's red and blue mascots, \Nthe Noppons, are brothers. Not lovers.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.56,0:09:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.02,0:09:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever. Tree, tower, it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.28,0:09:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all forgetting about Tanashi Tower!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.24,0:10:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The official name is "Skytower West Tokyo".
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.87,0:10:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is their mascot, Sorapon.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.83,0:10:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,"West Tokyo" is bad enough, but "Skytower"?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.25,0:10:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a perfect blend of the other two.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.51,0:10:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Anyway, I don't think there's any need for us \Nto trek out to Skytree or Tanashi Tower.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.68,0:10:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it enough to stand here and take in this scenery?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.93,0:10:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}The view to the north is amazing. \NThe light hits it just right and you can see everything.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.43,0:10:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see Mt. Fuji!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.73,0:10:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Haneda Airport to the south.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.81,0:10:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Where is it you can see \Nthe Rainbow Bridge? West? East?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.99,0:10:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Which do you like better, north or south?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.78,0:10:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,North. South. Which one is your favourite?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.45,0:10:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,North, I think.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.70,0:10:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm, I see. Why is that?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.04,0:10:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I just went with my gut.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.25,0:10:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.29,0:10:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so vague. It's not really a reason.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.34,0:10:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't the south better?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.80,0:10:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you—
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.51,0:11:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready to choose the North?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.43,0:11:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you prepared to never return to the South?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.68,0:11:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're t-talking about scenery, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.68,0:11:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Just talking about scenery.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.06,0:11:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}It's kind of hard to keep north, \Nsouth, east, and west straight.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.14,0:11:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}I just remember that north is up, south is down, \Nright is east, and left is west.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.15,0:11:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't left vs. right just as hard to remember?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.61,0:11:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Right is the chopstick hand. \NLeft is where I hold my rice bowl.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.49,0:11:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Which do you like better, right or left?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.74,0:11:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really know...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.33,0:11:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you lean to the right? Or the left?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.79,0:11:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.21,0:11:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You prefer the centre?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.50,0:11:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... uh...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.13,0:11:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(602.667,682.667)}Uh... uh...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.17,0:11:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(504,682.667)}Uh... uh...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.21,0:11:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(357.333,682.667)}Uh... uh...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.25,0:11:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(181.333,682.667)}Uh... uh...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.30,0:11:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(-13.333,682.667)}Uh... uh...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.50,0:11:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you tell us which one {\i1}you{\i0} like best?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.71,0:11:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? I like...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.59,0:11:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Down.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.97,0:11:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I like looking down.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.89,0:11:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Look, the Russian Embassy!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.73,0:11:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}The Netherlands, Fiji, Afghanistan... \NThere's a lot of embassies 'round here!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.65,0:12:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}How do you think non-Japanese people \Nremember their left and right?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.95,0:12:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Fork side and knife side?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.95,0:12:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}But don't you sometimes switch \Nyour fork to the other hand?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.79,0:12:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Like when you cut steak up first and then \Nswap your fork to their right hand to eat it.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.79,0:12:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you eat rice.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.00,0:12:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}By the way, what's up with people \Nwho put rice on the top of their fork?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.59,0:12:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you say "top" or "reverse"?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.01,0:12:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do they even eat rice overseas?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.88,0:12:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}I heard it was a holdover from table manners \Nwhen eating boiled beans.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.43,0:12:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's not wrong per se.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.43,0:12:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If you just scoop them up, they fall all over the place,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.56,0:12:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}so you're meant to help them onto \Nthe back of your fork using your knife.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.73,0:12:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Back? Of a fork?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.69,0:12:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The raised bit is called the back.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.69,0:12:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So the concave bit is the tummy?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.24,0:12:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}You'd expect the bit that \Nsticks out to be the tummy.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.11,0:12:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The back sticks out like Peko.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.53,0:12:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Peko? The Fujiya mascot?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.62,0:12:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Her tongue is sticking out.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.41,0:12:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So it is.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.41,0:12:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,When did they get a dog? They're so cheeky.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.79,0:12:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, they're just kids. It's fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.13,0:13:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So a fork is the opposite of a kid?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.38,0:13:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it doesn't stick out where it should.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.88,0:13:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see what you mean.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.55,0:13:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Marii is like a fork, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.64,0:13:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oi!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.39,0:13:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.48,0:13:15.06,Alt,,0,0,0,,Straight and narrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.06,0:13:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I guess you're right. I'm a very honest person.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.40,0:13:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Completely straight up and down.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.94,0:13:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Hold on, are you complimenting me \Nor insulting me? I can't tell!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.20,0:13:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is a lovely view.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.95,0:13:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see the Imperial Palace!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.45,0:13:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Comment: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:32.95,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Part C}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.50,0:13:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"But how did you eat the whole dessert?"
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.08,0:13:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,"It was a piece of cake!"
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.17,0:13:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your continued appreciation.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.72,0:13:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.85,0:13:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I have absolutely {\i1}no{\i0} idea what you're trying to say.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.98,0:13:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you tell?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.86,0:14:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make us explain such dull things!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.65,0:14:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, this new type of flu is scary.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.82,0:14:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true, but hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.28,0:14:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How long do we get to keep calling it a "new type"?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.20,0:14:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It started in winter and it's already summer.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.50,0:14:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we just going to keep pretending it's new?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.33,0:14:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}If a manga had been out that long \Nand they called it a new release,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.25,0:14:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,they'd be a laughing stock!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.42,0:14:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}A Shounen Jump series would \Nalready be finished by now!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.30,0:14:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}If it was an anime then the first cour would be over \Nand the DVD would already have come out!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.97,0:14:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Worst-case, everyone would have \Nalready forgotten about it!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.72,0:14:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Just accept that nobody's buying it!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.85,0:14:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,First impressions are everything!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.35,0:14:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Your numbers aren't going to improve!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.35,0:14:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to try something.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.40,0:14:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,One moment, please.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.49,0:14:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm New-Type Kukuru!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.49,0:14:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The new me!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.24,0:14:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly do you mean by "new type"?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.17,0:15:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, well...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.08,0:15:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She now emits pleasing scents from her nipples!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.96,0:15:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.00,0:15:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alphaH&FF&\t(0,200,\alphaH&00&\3a&HA0&)}Just give the screen a rub here.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.63,0:15:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It smells great!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.93,0:15:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Friendship perks?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.59,0:15:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Rubbing nipples has nothing to do with being friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.76,0:15:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds more like that John Waters film "Polyester".
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.77,0:15:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you've been rubbed already.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.48,0:15:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's been rubbing Kukuru?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.40,0:15:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Show yourself, culprit!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.31,0:15:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Anyway, what's the difference between \N"new type" and "old type"?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.53,0:15:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Sometimes they don't change anything but \Nthe packaging, then slap a "new" label on it.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.07,0:15:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,They do?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.99,0:15:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes they bring on substitute idol group members
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.62,0:15:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and tout the performance as a whole new cast.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.12,0:15:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They do!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.75,0:15:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Old types are heavy.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.83,0:15:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't even have cameras and stuff.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.25,0:15:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Do you really need there to be a camera?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.55,0:15:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you don't really!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.80,0:15:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't meet celebs in town that often.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.39,0:16:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}There's no need to keep people \Nupdated on your every movement.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.10,0:16:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Pay with cash.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.73,0:16:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A wallet is a wallet, a phone is a phone.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.48,0:16:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we even need new types of things?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.73,0:16:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.07,0:16:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What were we talking about again?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.57,0:16:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,New type, old type... Maybe it doesn't really matter.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.41,0:16:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We probably shouldn't be getting so worked up.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.70,0:16:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There are people laid up in bed with the flu right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.04,0:16:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, we should be trying not to catch it.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.29,0:16:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everyone vaccinated?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.54,0:16:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet. We're not that high a priority.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.92,0:16:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there an order?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.22,0:16:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.51,0:16:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctors are the first priority, I think.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.55,0:16:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they're the first line of defence against infection.
Dialogue: 9,0:16:40.52,0:16:43.19,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs32\shad0\pos(33.333,18.667)}Note: An inventor.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.52,0:16:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Does that include Dr. N*k*m*tsu?
Dialogue: 9,0:16:43.19,0:16:45.77,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs32\shad0\pos(33.333,18.667)}Note: A plastic surgeon.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.19,0:16:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Dr. T*k*su?
Dialogue: 9,0:16:45.77,0:16:47.06,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs32\shad0\pos(33.333,18.667)}Note: A psychiatrist.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.77,0:16:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Or Dr. K*y*m*?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.52,0:16:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}We probably come after Dr. Zhivago, \NDr. No and Dr. Moreau...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.95,0:16:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}No, this is only for proper doctors \Nwho deal directly with the flu.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.08,0:17:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Does that mean that Bl*ck J*ck won't get \Nvaccinated because he's not licensed?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.16,0:17:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the one most likely to cure the outbreak!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.50,0:17:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}No. For one thing, it'd be expensive. \NSecondly, he's not real.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.67,0:17:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}But there must be people who aren't doctors \Nwho've taken the vaccination drugs.
Dialogue: 9,0:17:13.55,0:17:22.72,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs32\shad0\pos(33.333,18.667)}Note: Japanese celebs with widely rumoured drug problems.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.55,0:17:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,N*ri-P definitely took the drugs!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.14,0:17:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,M*rcy definitely took the drugs!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.89,0:17:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Osh*o M*n*bu probably injected them with the drugs!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.72,0:17:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it was a pill.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.14,0:17:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Celebrities probably have secret ways to get \Npriority vaccinations, but I suppose we're out of luck.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.15,0:17:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We're neither rich nor famous.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.07,0:17:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one way.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.36,0:17:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Next on the list after doctors are...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.45,0:17:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Pregnant women.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.62,0:17:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ack! You're saying we should get pregnant?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.08,0:17:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}It's the only way to ensure \Nyou get priority vaccinations.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.83,0:17:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Kigu, do you know where babies come from?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.17,0:17:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Th-The pressure...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.88,0:17:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}If you smooch the boy you like, \NMr. Stork brings you a baby!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.84,0:18:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, you little cutie-pie.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.05,0:18:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine that you don't know.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.93,0:18:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\q2}Tch. I'm getting sick of playing into \Neveryone's expectations of me.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.39,0:18:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm, but getting pregnant...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.02,0:18:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not as simple as that.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.77,0:18:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one way.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.86,0:18:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They call it "false pregnancy".
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.90,0:18:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing in the rules against false pregnancy!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.03,0:18:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Virtual or real, it's pregnancy just the same!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.99,0:18:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a loophole in the law!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.16,0:18:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, time to visualise it.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.37,0:18:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.71,0:18:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Contemplate the mysteries of life.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.54,0:18:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The path of evolution.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.21,0:18:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that smile...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.67,0:18:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you imagining, you weirdo?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.72,0:18:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}H-Hey! I wasn't thinking about \Nthe process or anything of the kind!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.93,0:18:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She definitely was.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.68,0:18:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}It's no use! False pregnancy isn't \Ngoing to work. I can't imagine it at all!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.39,0:18:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you start with a false relationship?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.02,0:18:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Start with your first meeting.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.85,0:18:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's at a group blind date.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.73,0:18:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He asks you to meet up with him one-on-one.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.86,0:18:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And then?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.16,0:19:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Your relationship grows!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.74,0:19:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, we're fighting!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.49,0:19:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}He won't put the toilet seat down \Nwhen he's done using it!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.74,0:19:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But you make up—
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.20,0:19:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We're fighting again!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.33,0:19:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He's throwing an ashtray against the wall!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.04,0:19:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But you make up again!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.71,0:19:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He confides in one of his female friends...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.22,0:19:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Next thing I know, he's telling me \N"you'll be alright on your own".
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.05,0:19:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all so sudden! I'm so hurt!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.60,0:19:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Self-inflicted wounds.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.39,0:19:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.52,0:19:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, um...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.86,0:19:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,She's completely shut out all noise.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.74,0:19:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She's floating on a sea of imagination...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.20,0:19:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She's literally floating!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.45,0:19:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning sickness?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.41,0:19:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm craving something spicy!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.79,0:19:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.50,0:19:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought you some curried seafood!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.80,0:19:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That smells gross!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.92,0:20:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought you something spy-cy!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.05,0:20:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That was terrible.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.39,0:20:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought you a pile of lemons!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.55,0:20:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Just put them down there.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.81,0:20:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It moved!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.60,0:20:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Her mind has complete control over her body.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.10,0:20:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Are we sure she's not \N{\i1}actually{\i0} gonna give birth?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.44,0:20:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,My stomach somehow feels bigger.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.23,0:20:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you just ate too much at lunch.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.57,0:20:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Music.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.74,0:20:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Music?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.70,0:20:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Antenatal care?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.95,0:20:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Play something suitable!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.45,0:20:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Right away!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.13,0:20:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The fetus doesn't want to listen to anime trash!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.13,0:20:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows what that'll do to it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.01,0:20:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, I've decided to call her Pree T Cure.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.09,0:20:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe Milky.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.68,0:20:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Or Horizon—
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.10,0:20:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-She's coming!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.31,0:20:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's time!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.35,0:20:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Fetch some hot water!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.68,0:20:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Why are we going along with this?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.35,0:20:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}How dare you! The mother-to-be \Ncomes before everything!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.86,0:21:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I mean, that's an admirable sentiment, but—
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.40,0:21:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's a fundamental flaw.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.61,0:21:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's not actually pregnant.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.82,0:21:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,She's coming...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.41,0:21:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.87,0:21:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She passed out.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.83,0:21:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, show's over, guys.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.59,0:21:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing to see here.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.13,0:21:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what was going on.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.84,0:21:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, she's awake!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.68,0:21:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's my baby?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.35,0:21:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hush little one, go to sleep...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.36,0:21:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,My baby...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.11,0:21:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My baby...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.36,0:21:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait just a sec—
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.20,0:21:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me, ladies!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:02.38,0:22:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess she got priority treatment in the end.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.80,0:22:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure it's the kind of treatment she had in mind.
Comment: 0,0:23:39.93,0:23:39.93,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:40.89,0:23:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Kukuru Anrakutei here.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:42.69,0:23:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's outlook is:
Dialogue: 10,0:23:44.94,0:23:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:46.15,0:23:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So good it might go up in flames.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:50.57,0:23:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish everything would just disappear.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:53.16,0:23:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I wish I could just disappear.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:56.08,0:23:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the miraculous third episode of Rakugo Girls:
Dialogue: 10,0:23:58.95,0:24:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}"Bath of Last Resort", "Asakusa Visit", \Nand "A Stroke of Raku".
Dialogue: 10,0:24:04.58,0:24:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Until then, look after your bodies.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:07.88,0:24:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay healthy.
